# Netlify _redirects file
# Redirects greececyclades.com to discovercyclades.gr
# IMPORTANT: Googlebot tries HTTP first, so handle HTTP → HTTPS → New Domain

# Step 1: Redirect HTTP to HTTPS (same domain)
http://greececyclades.com/*    https://greececyclades.com/:splat    301!
http://www.greececyclades.com/*    https://www.greececyclades.com/:splat    301!

# Step 2: Redirect HTTPS to new domain
https://greececyclades.com/*   https://discovercyclades.gr/:splat    301!
https://www.greececyclades.com/*   https://discovercyclades.gr/:splat    301!

